trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoEnumerator"></xref> class provides enumeration functionality for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoEnumerator.Current"></xref> property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object that represents the current recipient information structure in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoEnumerator.MoveNext"></xref> method advances the enumeration to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
This method returns a bool that specifies whether the enumeration successfully advanced.
If the enumeration successfully moved to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object, the method returns `true`.
If the enumeration moved past the last item in the enumeration, it returns `false`.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoEnumerator.Reset"></xref> method resets the enumeration to the first <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.

The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoEnumerator.System#Collections#IEnumerator#Current"></xref> property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfo"></xref> object that represents the current recipient information structure in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.RecipientInfoCollection"></xref> collection.
